name: Steve Whaley
text: Very good! This was our first time here. We ordered pizzas, bread sticks, and potato wedges. Everything was hot, fresh, and delicious. We definitely will do this again soon.

name: James Ginotti
text: Love there pizza. Staff is always nice

name: Tammy Warner
text: Love their pizza and food! Excellent

name: Mistie Keen
text: Love the pizza! People! And all the choices for a lunch on my way to work a late shift!  Wonderful woman owns and operates thus business!  Everyone's friendly.
